WEBVTT

00:01:29.298 --> 00:01:33.112
and how we all have an innate
understanding of its materiality

00:01:33.136 --> 00:01:34.476
through breathing.

00:01:36.530 --> 00:01:42.190
All life on Earth changes the air
through gas exchange,

00:01:42.214 --> 00:01:43.975
and we're all doing it right now.

00:01:44.679 --> 00:01:47.647
Actually, why don't we all
right now together take

00:01:47.671 --> 00:01:50.432
one big, collective, deep breath in.

00:01:50.456 --> 00:01:52.835
Ready? In. (Inhales)

00:01:55.009 --> 00:01:56.807
And out. (Exhales)

00:01:58.782 --> 00:02:01.452
That air that you just exhaled,